<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>School Rules</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.7.2/css/all.min.css">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      color: #222;
    }

    .hero img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
    }

    .rules-card {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 50px;
      margin: 60px 90px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .rules {
      flex: 1 1 500px;
    }

    .rules h1 {
      color: #0288d1;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    .rules li {
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-size: 17px;
      font-weight: 500;
      word-break: normal;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }

    .img {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .img img {
      border-radius: 7px;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 450px;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
      margin: 0 auto 15px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    }

    .img p {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: #046ca4;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* 🔹 Responsive Design 🔹 */
    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .rules-card {
        margin: 40px 50px;
        gap: 30px;
      }

      .rules li {
        font-size: 16px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .rules-card {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: left;
        margin: 30px 20px;
      }

      .rules h1 {
        text-align: center;
      }

      .rules li {
        font-size: 15px;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      .img img {
        max-width: 100%;
      }

      .img p {
        font-size: 18px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .rules h1 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }

      .rules li {
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .img p {
        font-size: 16px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <%- include("partials/HomePageSchoolName") %>
  <%- include("partials/HomePageNavbar") %>

  <section class="hero">
    <img src="images/img2.png" alt="Rishikulam School Building">
  </section>

  <section class="rules-card">
    <ul class="rules">
      <h1>SCHOOL RULES</h1>
      <li>The students are supposed to reach the school premises 10 minutes before the assembly starts.</li>
      <li>The students should attend the assembly compulsorily.</li>
      <li>The students should maintain strict discipline in the school premises and observe good manners.</li>
      <li>Students should be neatly dressed and should attend the school in the prescribed uniform only.</li>
      <li>Every student should take care of the school property.</li>
      <li>Expensive materials and things should not be brought to school.</li>
      <li>Students should not borrow or lend the money in the school.</li>
      <li>Criticism of the teacher, personnel and school in the presence of a child should be avoided.</li>
      <li>Boys are required to have a formal haircut. No designs are allowed.</li>
      <li>Putting “mehandi” and keeping long nails is prohibited for the girls.</li>
      <li>Shouting, whistling, running etc. in corridors are strictly prohibited.</li>
      <li>The Students should bring nutritious food in the Tiffin and lunch box.</li>
      <li>Students should actively participate in all school activities.</li>
       <li>Students should attend all the functions celebrated in the School.</li>
       <li>Students suffering from any contagious disease will not be allowed to continue classes until he/she recovers from it.</li>
      <li>The School bag must contain text books and note books of the prescribed time table, required material along with the School Diary.</li>    
      <li>All parents are expected to attend every PTM (Parents Teachers Meeting) of the School.</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="img">
      <img src="images/img5.jpg" alt="Motivational Image">
      <p>Build Your Future</p>
      <img src="images/library.jpg" alt="Students Image">
    </div>
  </section>

  <%- include("partials/HomePageContact") %>
  <%- include("partials/HomePageFooter") %>
</body>

</html>
